      <title>美国和韩国本周将就美军费用举行会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-south-korea-meet-american-troop-costs-this-week-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务院周一表示，美国和韩国官员将于本周在夏威夷举行会谈，讨论分担驻韩美军的费用，美国寻求“公平公正的结果”，以加强两国的联盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-south-korea-meet-american-troop-costs-this-week-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 22:04:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
